high_descs: Head straight to the sink, take a bar of soap from the sink
Turn around, head to the black table
Open the top drawer of the table
put the soap in the drawer
close the drawer to the table
Take the soap from on top of the black table
Open the top drawer of the table
put the soap in the drawer, close the drawer to the table
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the drawer of the black table

high_descs: Walk up to the sink in front of you.
Pick up the rightmost bar of soap out of the sink basin.
Turn left and walk up to the tub, then turn left and walk over to the small black table.
Open the drawer of the table and put the bar of soap in in the back left corner then close the drawer.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the small black table.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the small black table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the tub, turn left again to face the small black table.
Open the drawer of the table and put the bar of soap inside to the right of the bar that's already in there, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap into a drawer.

high_descs: Walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the right side soap on the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the desk.
Place the soap in the right drawer of the desk.
Step to the right to face the soap on the desk.
Pick up the soap on the desk.
Step right to face the right drawer of the desk.
Put the soap in the desk next to the first soap.
anns.task_desc: To put two bars of soap in the right drawer of a desk.
